      <h1>Forskrift om ikke-samarbeidsvillige jurisdiksjoner for skatteform&#xE5;l</h1>
      <article class="legalArticle" data-lovdata-URL="LTI/forskrift/2025-07-01-1379/&#xA7;1" data-name="&#xA7;1" id="paragraf-1">
        <h2 class="legalArticleHeader"><span class="legalArticleValue">&#xA7; 1</span>. <span class="legalArticleTitle">Form&#xE5;l</span></h2>
        <article class="legalP" id="paragraf-1-ledd-1">Forskriftens form&#xE5;l er &#xE5; oppfylle E&#xD8;S-rettslige forpliktelser ved &#xE5; fastsette en liste over ikke-samarbeidsvillige jurisdiksjoner som tar st&#xF8;rst mulig hensyn til EUs liste over ikke-samarbeidsvillige jurisdiksjoner for skattemessige form&#xE5;l.</article>
      </article>
      <article class="legalArticle" data-lovdata-URL="LTI/forskrift/2025-07-01-1379/&#xA7;2" data-name="&#xA7;2" id="paragraf-2">
        <h2 class="legalArticleHeader"><span class="legalArticleValue">&#xA7; 2</span>. <span class="legalArticleTitle">Revisjon av forskriften</span></h2>
        <article class="legalP" id="paragraf-2-ledd-1">Departementet skal, ved eventuelle endringer i EUs liste over ikke-samarbeidsvillige jurisdiksjoner for skattemessige form&#xE5;l, vurdere endringene og gj&#xF8;re tilsvarende endringer i &#xA7;&#xA7; 3 eller 4. Ved vurderingen av om stater oppf&#xF8;rt p&#xE5; EUs liste skal f&#xF8;res opp p&#xE5; listene i &#xA7;&#xA7; 3 eller 4, skal departementet ta i betraktning i hvilken grad Norge inng&#xE5;r i forpliktende internasjonalt samarbeid med statene.</article>
      </article>
      <article class="legalArticle" data-lovdata-URL="LTI/forskrift/2025-07-01-1379/&#xA7;3" data-name="&#xA7;3" id="paragraf-3">
        <h2 class="legalArticleHeader"><span class="legalArticleValue">&#xA7; 3</span>. <span class="legalArticleTitle">Stater oppf&#xF8;rt i vedlegg I over ikke-samarbeidsvillige jurisdiksjoner for skattemessige form&#xE5;l</span></h2>
        <article class="legalP" id="paragraf-3-ledd-1">F&#xF8;lgende stater er oppf&#xF8;rt i vedlegg I over ikke-samarbeidsvillige jurisdiksjoner for skattemessige form&#xE5;l:<ul class="defaultList"><li data-li-identifier="1." data-name="1."><article class="listArticle" id="paragraf-3-ledd-1-punkt-1"><article class="legalP" id="paragraf-3-ledd-1-punkt-1-ledd-1">Amerikansk Samoa</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="2." data-name="2."><article class="listArticle" id="paragraf-3-ledd-1-punkt-2"><article class="legalP" id="paragraf-3-ledd-1-punkt-2-ledd-1">Anguilla</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="3." data-name="3."><article class="listArticle" id="paragraf-3-ledd-1-punkt-3"><article class="legalP" id="paragraf-3-ledd-1-punkt-3-ledd-1">Fiji</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="4." data-name="4."><article class="listArticle" id="paragraf-3-ledd-1-punkt-4"><article class="legalP" id="paragraf-3-ledd-1-punkt-4-ledd-1">Guam</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="5." data-name="5."><article class="listArticle" id="paragraf-3-ledd-1-punkt-5"><article class="legalP" id="paragraf-3-ledd-1-punkt-5-ledd-1">Palau</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="6." data-name="6."><article class="listArticle" id="paragraf-3-ledd-1-punkt-6"><article class="legalP" id="paragraf-3-ledd-1-punkt-6-ledd-1">Panama</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="7." data-name="7."><article class="listArticle" id="paragraf-3-ledd-1-punkt-7"><article class="legalP" id="paragraf-3-ledd-1-punkt-7-ledd-1">Russland</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="8." data-name="8."><article class="listArticle" id="paragraf-3-ledd-1-punkt-8"><article class="legalP" id="paragraf-3-ledd-1-punkt-8-ledd-1">Samoa</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="9." data-name="9."><article class="listArticle" id="paragraf-3-ledd-1-punkt-9"><article class="legalP" id="paragraf-3-ledd-1-punkt-9-ledd-1">Trinidad og Tobago</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="10." data-name="10."><article class="listArticle" id="paragraf-3-ledd-1-punkt-10"><article class="legalP" id="paragraf-3-ledd-1-punkt-10-ledd-1">De amerikanske Jomfru&#xF8;yene</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="11." data-name="11."><article class="listArticle" id="paragraf-3-ledd-1-punkt-11"><article class="legalP" id="paragraf-3-ledd-1-punkt-11-ledd-1">Vanuatu.</article></article></li></ul></article>
      </article>
      <article class="legalArticle" data-lovdata-URL="LTI/forskrift/2025-07-01-1379/&#xA7;4" data-name="&#xA7;4" id="paragraf-4">
        <h2 class="legalArticleHeader"><span class="legalArticleValue">&#xA7; 4</span>. <span class="legalArticleTitle">Stater oppf&#xF8;rt i vedlegg II over ikke-samarbeidsvillige jurisdiksjoner for skattemessige form&#xE5;l</span></h2>
        <article class="legalP" id="paragraf-4-ledd-1">F&#xF8;lgende stater er oppf&#xF8;rt i vedlegg II over ikke-samarbeidsvillige jurisdiksjoner for skattemessige form&#xE5;l:<ul class="defaultList"><li data-li-identifier="1." data-name="1."><article class="listArticle" id="paragraf-4-ledd-1-punkt-1"><article class="legalP" id="paragraf-4-ledd-1-punkt-1-ledd-1">Antigua og Barbuda</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="2." data-name="2."><article class="listArticle" id="paragraf-4-ledd-1-punkt-2"><article class="legalP" id="paragraf-4-ledd-1-punkt-2-ledd-1">Belize</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="3." data-name="3."><article class="listArticle" id="paragraf-4-ledd-1-punkt-3"><article class="legalP" id="paragraf-4-ledd-1-punkt-3-ledd-1">De britiske Jomfru&#xF8;yene</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="4." data-name="4."><article class="listArticle" id="paragraf-4-ledd-1-punkt-4"><article class="legalP" id="paragraf-4-ledd-1-punkt-4-ledd-1">Brunei</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="5." data-name="5."><article class="listArticle" id="paragraf-4-ledd-1-punkt-5"><article class="legalP" id="paragraf-4-ledd-1-punkt-5-ledd-1">Eswatini</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="6." data-name="6."><article class="listArticle" id="paragraf-4-ledd-1-punkt-6"><article class="legalP" id="paragraf-4-ledd-1-punkt-6-ledd-1">Seychellene</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="7." data-name="7."><article class="listArticle" id="paragraf-4-ledd-1-punkt-7"><article class="legalP" id="paragraf-4-ledd-1-punkt-7-ledd-1">Tyrkia</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="8." data-name="8."><article class="listArticle" id="paragraf-4-ledd-1-punkt-8"><article class="legalP" id="paragraf-4-ledd-1-punkt-8-ledd-1">Vietnam.</article></article></li></ul></article>
      </article>
      <article class="legalArticle" data-lovdata-URL="LTI/forskrift/2025-07-01-1379/&#xA7;5" data-name="&#xA7;5" id="paragraf-5">
